#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Pabbatavagga"
msgstr "1. Mountains"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 7. Kūṭāgārasutta → kūṭa (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Kūṭāgārasutta"
msgstr "7. A Bungalow"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.7:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa yā kāci gopānasiyo, sabbā tā kūṭaninnā "
"kūṭapoṇā kūṭapabbhārā;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the rafters of a bungalow all slant, slope, and incline to the "
"peak."

msgctxt "sn46.7:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the seven awakening "
"factors slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.76"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.7:2.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the seven awakening factors slant, "
"slope, and incline to extinguishment?"

msgctxt "sn46.7:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, "
"investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and "
"equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen "
"as letting go."

msgctxt "sn46.7:2.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the seven awakening "
"factors slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.7:2.4"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
